==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionThreadHoleSide''' tool adds a cosmetic thread to the side view of a hole.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleSideExample.png|200px]]
{{Caption|On the right a hole with a cosmetic thread}}

==Usage==

# Optionally specify the line attributes with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select two parallel lines.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleSide.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleSide|Add Cosmetic Thread Hole Side View]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Centerlines/Threading → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleSide.svg|16px]] Add Cosmetic Thread Hole Side View}} option from the menu.
# A cosmetic thread is added.


